Title: Robinson Willey gas tap kit
Description: This Robinson Willey gas tap kit is for use in the gas valve section of Robinson Willey Firegem Visa Highline LPG, Firegem Visa 2 Dl Highline and Firegem Visa Dl Highline gas fires.  Controlled by the unit's PCB, the gas valve regulates gas flow, opening up to allow gas into the pilot assembly or burner, depending on the model of the appliance, where needed.
